Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:23.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}鄰家的南先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近冬馬總是回來得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這丫頭也有自己的交際圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從新交了個叫作「千秋」的朋友才這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和咱家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓氏是「南」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願別是個不好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬要晚些回來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊可是很周到地打電話來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來這陣子嘴巴倒是更刻薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有些男孩子氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天對著沒出息的哥哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就比別人更加男孩子氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才那番話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己也算進去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有心儀的男孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡的男孩不該是更有女人味兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對家人變得冷淡也挺正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的南家似乎有三個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好有個帥氣的大哥哥之類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這帥氣的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱家就已經夠多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎說什麼呢  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟著冬馬一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南家調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？讓我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊留冬馬吃了好幾回飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們好歹也得表示一下謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿禮數作障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（翌日）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天哥哥跟我一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他先在外頭等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  你家也真夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可受了不少罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來春香似乎心情很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看他們都是認為咱家不可信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你有沒有認真在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說電話裏我那尖嗓子很可疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  剛才說的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說冬馬家很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在外頭等著的那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他進來你哥哥們也就不會再擔無謂的心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冬馬的哥哥秋良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹一直以來承蒙你們照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點小意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真夠小意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為憑幾塊肥皂就可以打發我們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這大談特談少女心的三少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  你都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼就說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱大姐頭的心情可不會因為幾塊肥皂就好起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好像變好了些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道冬馬在這兒過得怎麼樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就像對待冬馬一樣來招待你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你改作盤腿坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：較正式的場合為跪坐）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冬馬一起留下來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吃得丁點兒不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我們都姓南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你小子知道知道誰比較配姓南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說這話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展是否順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  這裏是南家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南冬馬家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是南千秋的姐姐南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬君和秋良君在我這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  這調子也太低沉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼扯到這個話題的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你說自己無論如何都想要個女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過這話？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還真說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常想怎麼樣才能有個女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數學課之類的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很認真地思考這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要看看我的數學筆記？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像上面寫滿了令人生厭的秋良方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,π等於2h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來談談你喜歡的類型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了夏奈  隨便是誰都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你得先明白我對你沒有意思再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我按順序來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我弄錯順序了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家春香怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她給我的第一印象是恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那一頭長髮倒是不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒有個正合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡君的小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去和南同學關係不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他倆到底是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  若無其事地和南同學搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若～無其事地問他們的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你喜歡的類型了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要交給本小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像氣勢洶洶地瞪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈同學  那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠太近了靠太近了靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是頭兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…頭兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳下功夫相當了得哦  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會…會被踹死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這氛圍不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地走過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不能若無其事地搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是剛才那位黑髮美女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:08:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是頭兒的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盯著她看得出神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以頭兒不樂意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對別人的女朋友下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話我還是喜歡夏奈同學這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先這麼著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說要和我比試比試對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我你的班級和名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡君難得一見的神情的小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋良那傢伙最近沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次來咱家的冬馬的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是學校裏有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  看我讓他振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊  笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一個笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…很有意思的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字就叫山田了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那還真是了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把勁兒  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊  我家那口子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一道關口  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先下腳為強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂餵這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食慾魔人千秋大人居然吃不下飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田他坐卡車走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦  人生正所謂聚散離合嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不都因為你  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你做了什麼是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還莫名其妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我壓根兒就不認識什麼山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來打排球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二哥夏樹原本挺好動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從參加社團活動之後就老實多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再來一碗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得好像是排球部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說他總是挺早回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來接冬馬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼自己都吃得這麼帶勁兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再添一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能參加練習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天得回去做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  這是我做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這便當是否配得上我最愛的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓你嘗嘗味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給女生做便當能讓她開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛吃過飯  現在還飽著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能說得上什麼感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不是你的午餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是留著待會兒吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留著待會兒吃的不能現在打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能現在吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道女生喜歡什麼味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼不瞭解女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女生視為未知的生物一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹真是座冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又整出個怪裏怪氣的嘍囉來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹  你來二年級的教室有事兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟妹妹承蒙南春香同學款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以過來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是個挺重視禮儀的傢伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來參加社團活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排球部的男生很悲慘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得有人告訴保阪學長罰跑操場50圈是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得回家做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是找春香有事兒對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大概知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然眾目睽睽之下很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至想現在就跑開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不做個了斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱倆彼此都不痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我試試味兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芋頭栗子和松菇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很有秋天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣香味就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得多吸收鐵質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐菜刀的聲音亂了分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出什麼事兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在學校見到春香了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見倒是見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻惹出麻煩來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事兒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學之後我去千秋家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  借這個機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實春香算是很懶的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在犯懶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒人讓她提起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是相當懶的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天春香是最早回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香當時是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「先睡一覺吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不過還是先換衣服再睡吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「算了算了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「太麻煩了  就這麼睡吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道她是這麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三顆扣子半扣半開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想解開卻又放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我二哥想來和你們打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在在外頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫他進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不禮貌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冬馬的哥哥夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些天真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹承蒙你平日的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  這樣很不禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抬起頭來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你是冬馬的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這你都沒告訴人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  前些天的事情不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抬起頭來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很不禮貌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你也有失禮之處人家才不好抬起頭來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度的身體接觸就動手確實有些過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是嚇了一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在創造傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  衣服  衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若無其事地提醒過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的舊傷又發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止不住血  止不住血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就幫你止血  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快擦乾  快擦乾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  衣服  衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾  要多吸收鐵質哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  我也想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  下次是聖誕節的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說讓我去扮作南春香的聖誕老人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  得先準備上乘的服裝和馴鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:42.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向一流的聖誕老人看齊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  聖誕節啊聖誕夜啊

